data.description: Open house schedule for Sunday April 28th 1-3 PM VA assumable 3% home loan. This Incredible farmhouse style ranch home includes 4 bed, 3  baths and large 3 car garage. Zero entry front door opens to large living room with large linear fireplace, floating shelves and shiplap accents.  Kitchen includes  8 1/2 ft island with granite counter tops, generous dining area and walk-in pantry.  Laundry is just off the drop zone and interior garage door. Private primary Suite has coffered ceilings and bath consist of soaker tub, separate tiled shower, large walk-in closet and private water closet. Finished basement consists of a 4th bedroom, extensive family room with wet bar, space for mini or wine frig and wine rack and ample unfinished storage or space for additional finish.  6ft. iron fence surrounds .39 acre lot. Sellers are related to listing agent.
